{{Infobox official post |post = [[Permanent Representative]] |body = [[Greece]] to the [[North Atlantic Treaty Organization]] |native_name = Μόνιμος Αντιπρόσωπος της Ελλάδας στο ΝΑΤΟ |insignia = NATO flag.svg |insigniasize = 150px |insigniacaption = |department = |image = |alt = |incumbent = [[Spyros Lampridis]] |incumbentsince = {{dts|2016|01|01}} |style = His/Her [[Excellency]] |residence = |nominator = |nominatorpost = |appointer = |appointerpost = |termlength = |inaugural = [[Panagiotis Pipinelis]] |formation = {{dts|1952||}} |last = |abolished = |succession = |deputy = |salary = |website = }}
The '''Permanent Representative of Greece to NATO''' ({{lang-el|Μόνιμος Αντιπρόσωπος της Ελλάδας στο ΝΑΤΟ}}) is the [[Permanent Representative]] of the [[Greece|Greek]] government to the [[North Atlantic Council]].
{| class="wikitable sortable" !| [[Diplomatic accreditation]] !| [[Permanent Representative]] !| [[Greek language]] !| Observations !| [[Prime Minister of Greece]] !| Term end
