== Evolution of Dominions to Independence ==
{| class="wikitable sortable"
|-
! Country
! Date of Dominion Status
! Date of adoption of the [[Statute of Westminster 1931|Statute of Westminster]]
! Date of final relinquish of British powers
! Final Event in question.
